channel.title: Does anyone know what this weird thing in msn is?
channel.description:
I was in a group conversation, and a couple strange messages came up. The messages were like from a person, but it was in a different style to everybody else - smaller etc. There was nobody in the conversation with the name 'mod' Everybody denied knowing what it was. I screenied them and threw them together in a picture.
[URL=http://img525.imageshack.us/my.php?image=wthse1.png][IMG]http://img525.imageshack.us/img525/5471/wthse1.th.png[/img][/URL]
Does anyone know what this is?
